metadata.name: Api::V1::Accounts::StatusesController GET #index with someone else's pinned statuses when user follows account lists both the public and the private statuses

sql_query.sql: SELECT 1 AS one FROM "oauth_access_tokens" WHERE "oauth_access_tokens"."token" = $1 LIMIT $2
SELECT 1 AS one FROM "oauth_access_tokens" WHERE "oauth_access_tokens"."token" = $1 AND "oauth_access_tokens"."id" != $2 LIMIT $3
SELECT 1 AS one FROM "blocks" WHERE "blocks"."account_id" = $1 AND "blocks"."target_account_id" = $2 LIMIT $3
SELECT 1 AS one FROM "follows" WHERE "follows"."account_id" = $1 AND "follows"."target_account_id" = $2 LIMIT $3

SELECT "statuses"."id", "statuses"."updated_at" FROM "statuses" INNER JOIN "status_pins" ON "statuses"."id" = "status_pins"."status_id" LEFT OUTER JOIN "mentions" ON "mentions"."status_id" = "statuses"."id" LEFT OUTER JOIN "statuses" "reblog" ON "reblog"."deleted_at" IS NULL AND "reblog"."id" = "statuses"."reblog_of_id" LEFT OUTER JOIN "accounts" ON "accounts"."id" = "reblog"."account_id" WHERE "statuses"."account_id" = $1 AND ("statuses"."visibility" IN ($2, $3, $4) OR "mentions"."account_id" = $5) AND ("statuses"."reblog_of_id" IS NULL OR ("accounts"."domain" IS NULL OR 1=1) AND 1=1) AND "statuses"."deleted_at" IS NULL AND "status_pins"."account_id" = $6 GROUP BY "statuses"."id", "status_pins"."created_at" ORDER BY status_pins.created_at DESC, "statuses"."id" DESC LIMIT $7
SELECT "statuses".* FROM "statuses" WHERE "statuses"."deleted_at" IS NULL AND "statuses"."id" IN ($1, $2) ORDER BY "statuses"."id" DESC
SELECT "media_attachments".* FROM "media_attachments" WHERE "media_attachments"."status_id" IN ($1, $2) ORDER BY "media_attachments"."id" ASC

sql_query.sql: SELECT "custom_filter_keywords"."id" AS t0_r0, "custom_filter_keywords"."custom_filter_id" AS t0_r1, "custom_filter_keywords"."keyword" AS t0_r2, "custom_filter_keywords"."whole_word" AS t0_r3, "custom_filter_keywords"."created_at" AS t0_r4, "custom_filter_keywords"."updated_at" AS t0_r5, "custom_filter"."id" AS t1_r0, "custom_filter"."account_id" AS t1_r1, "custom_filter"."expires_at" AS t1_r2, "custom_filter"."phrase" AS t1_r3, "custom_filter"."context" AS t1_r4, "custom_filter"."created_at" AS t1_r5, "custom_filter"."updated_at" AS t1_r6, "custom_filter"."action" AS t1_r7 FROM "custom_filter_keywords" LEFT OUTER JOIN "custom_filters" "custom_filter" ON "custom_filter"."id" = "custom_filter_keywords"."custom_filter_id" WHERE "custom_filter"."account_id" = $1 AND (expires_at IS NULL OR expires_at > NOW())

SELECT "custom_filter_statuses"."id" AS t0_r0, "custom_filter_statuses"."custom_filter_id" AS t0_r1, "custom_filter_statuses"."status_id" AS t0_r2, "custom_filter_statuses"."created_at" AS t0_r3, "custom_filter_statuses"."updated_at" AS t0_r4, "custom_filter"."id" AS t1_r0, "custom_filter"."account_id" AS t1_r1, "custom_filter"."expires_at" AS t1_r2, "custom_filter"."phrase" AS t1_r3, "custom_filter"."context" AS t1_r4, "custom_filter"."created_at" AS t1_r5, "custom_filter"."updated_at" AS t1_r6, "custom_filter"."action" AS t1_r7 FROM "custom_filter_statuses" LEFT OUTER JOIN "custom_filters" "custom_filter" ON "custom_filter"."id" = "custom_filter_statuses"."custom_filter_id" WHERE "custom_filter"."account_id" = $1 AND (expires_at IS NULL OR expires_at > NOW())
